meta.name: AA Insurance Location Location Location NZ
meta.description: The worldwide smash-hit series returns to New Zealand! Trusted property experts, Jayne Kiely and Paul Glover help house hunting Kiwi navigate the real estate market and match them with their dream home!

videos.title: Episode 7
videos.overview: Jayne is on the hunt with Pritha and Valentina, an adventurous young couple who're ready to take the property plunge and Paul's helping the Farnell's to upsize with their granddaughter Sophie.
